#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn13.1"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn13.1:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 13 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 13 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.1:0.2"
msgid "1. Abhisamayavagga "
msgstr "1. Comprehension "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn13.1:0.3"
msgid "1. Nakhasikhāsutta "
msgstr "1. A Fingernail "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn13.1:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "sn13.1:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.1:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā parittaṃ nakhasikhāyaṃ paṃsuṃ āropetvā bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "Then the Buddha, picking up a little bit of dirt under his fingernail, addressed the mendicants: "

msgctxt "sn13.1:1.4"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "“What do you think, mendicants? "

#. VAR: vāyaṃ → yo cāyaṃ (si, s1-3, pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn13.1:1.5"
msgid "katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ, yo vāyaṃ mayā paritto nakhasikhāyaṃ paṃsu āropito, ayaṃ vā mahāpathavī”ti? "
msgstr "Which is more: the little bit of dirt under my fingernail, or this great earth?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.134, sc2
msgctxt "sn13.1:2.1"
msgid "“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ, yadidaṃ mahāpathavī. "
msgstr "“Sir, the great earth is far more. "

msgctxt "sn13.1:2.2"
msgid "Appamattako bhagavatā paritto nakhasikhāyaṃ paṃsu āropito. "
msgstr "The little bit of dirt under your fingernail is tiny. "

msgctxt "sn13.1:2.3"
msgid "Neva satimaṃ kalaṃ upeti na sahassimaṃ kalaṃ upeti na satasahassimaṃ kalaṃ upeti mahāpathaviṃ upanidhāya bhagavatā paritto nakhasikhāyaṃ paṃsu āropito”ti. "
msgstr "Compared to the great earth, it’s not nearly a hundredth, a thousandth, or a hundred thousandth part.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.1:2.4"
msgid "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa diṭṭhisampannassa puggalassa abhisametāvino etadeva bahutaraṃ dukkhaṃ yadidaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādiṇṇaṃ; "
msgstr "“In the same way, for a noble disciple accomplished in view, a person with comprehension, the suffering that’s over and done with is more, "

msgctxt "sn13.1:2.5"
msgid "appamattakaṃ avasiṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr "what’s left is tiny. "

msgctxt "sn13.1:2.6"
msgid "Neva satimaṃ kalaṃ upeti na sahassimaṃ kalaṃ upeti na satasahassimaṃ kalaṃ upeti purimaṃ dukkhakkhandhaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādiṇṇaṃ upanidhāya yadidaṃ sattakkhattuṃparamatā. "
msgstr "Compared to the mass of suffering in the past that’s over and done with, it’s not nearly a hundredth, a thousandth, or a hundred thousandth part, since there are at most seven more lives. "

msgctxt "sn13.1:2.7"
msgid "Evaṃ mahatthiyo kho, bhikkhave, dhammābhisamayo; "
msgstr "That’s how very beneficial it is to comprehend the teaching "

msgctxt "sn13.1:2.8"
msgid "evaṃ mahatthiyo dhammacakkhupaṭilābho”ti. "
msgstr "and gain the vision of the teaching.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn13.1:2.9"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

